description: There is a new boss in the office, but it’s not who anyone expected. When this team of factory workers lively hood is on the line they are willing to do whatever it takes to keep their jobs. Lexi has taken over and is extremely demanding. She has some serious standards for her employees in order for her to be satisfied with their work. She commands they all team up together and fill ever single hole at the same time and please her in a way that none of her employees ever have before.
title: Lexi Lore Gets DP and Gangbanged
